copy from source: buffer of 4 i32 to destination: buffer of 4 i32 does:
  let i be 0
  while i is less than 4:
    destination at i becomes source at i
    i becomes i plus 1

sum buffer cells: buffer of 4 i32 gives i32:
  let total be 0
  let i be 0
  while i is less than 4:
    total becomes total plus cells at i
    i becomes i plus 1
  total

main gives i32:
  let source be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 3
  let destination be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 0
  copy from source to destination
  sum buffer destination
